latestPosts.caption: Our products are made with premium ingredients and held to the highest standards in the industry. From our land in Fort Atkinson, WI to your skillet, microwave, oven or air fryer at home, make mealtime better with Jones!
From breakfast to dinner and snacking in between, Jones Canadian Bacon brings real flavor and, with 10g of protein per serving, real fuel.
latestPosts.alt: Photo by Jones Dairy Farm on July 07, 2025. May be an image of toast, plate, meat and text that says 'Jones Powers your Plate 10g Protein Per Serving Certified GlutenFree Gluten Free Minimal Ingredients ents MUAES'.

latestPosts.caption: 🏕️🥓 Looking for an even better way to do s’mores? Jones Dry Aged Bacon + melty chocolate + gooey marshmallow = the ultimate sweet-and-salty bite. Trust us—you’ll never go back.

Going to a backyard hang or having guests over for brunch? This red, white & blue board full of Jones favorites is perfect for the holiday weekend. 🇺🇸

🎇Happy 4th of July!🎆
😍 We love hearing positive feedback like this. Thank you so much for singing the praises of Jones Canadian Bacon, and for trusting us at your table all these years.

At Jones Dairy Farm, being family-owned means doing things differently. Philip Jones, our CEO and 6th generation family member, puts it simply—we don’t answer to shareholders, we answer to our customers. That’s why we never cut corners or skimp on ingredients just to save a buck.
latestPosts.alt: Photo by Jones Dairy Farm on June 30, 2025. May be an image of 1 person, office and text.

latestPosts.caption: Looking for a don’t-feel-like-making-dinner dinner? With a bag of our No Antibiotics Ever Meatballs in the freezer, you always have dinner at the ready.
Chicken, turkey or pork. Boxes or resealable bags. Pick your protein, pick your size, and enjoy the flavor of our All Natural Golden Brown Sausage. Find it near you!

Our All Natural Sausage Roll has been made the same way for nearly 200 years. Just pork, salt and spices. That’s it! Made on our original land in Fort Atkinson, WI. You won’t find finely crafted sausage like this from anyone but Jones.
latestPosts.alt: Photo by Jones Dairy Farm on June 26, 2025. May be an image of salami, sausage and text.

latestPosts.caption: Our All Natural Turkey, Chicken or Pork Sausage is juicy and delicious however you heat it. Sizzling in a pan, in the microwave or slightly crispy from the air fryer. Find it, and enjoy it, at a store near you!
